PrecisAppointment of a temporary Administrator, namely Mr. Justice HERBERT B. MORGAN, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Newfoundland, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of NEWFOUNDLAND over the course of a two-day period in October, 1991 (25th to the 26th).
